title: 99:  Potential Draft Trades & Mid-Round Gems
itunes:title: 99:  Potential Draft Trades & Mid-Round Gems
description:
Former NFL Scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks give you their perfect two picks for teams in the NFC and AFC West. The guys also analyze trades they want to see in the 2016 NFL Draft. DJ and Bucky then fill you in on mid-round draft steals.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
